---
import '@fontsource-variable/onest'

import Header from "@/components/Header.astro";
import Section from "@/components/Section.astro";
import Card from "@/components/Card.astro";
import Technologies from "@/components/Technologies.astro";
import Experience from "@/components/Experience.astro";
import SocialPill from '@/components/SocialPill.astro'
import GitHub from '@/components/icons/GitHub.astro'
import LinkedIn from '@/components/icons/LinkedIn.astro'
import BriefCaseIcon from '@/components/icons/BriefCaseIcon.astro'
import UserStarIcon from '@/components/icons/UserStarIcon.astro'
import CodeIcon from '@/components/icons/CodeIcon.astro'

import { projects, experience } from "@/data";
---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Alan Mayorga - Programador y Desarrollador Web</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Contrata a Alan Mayorga para crear aplicaciones web o moviles. Especializado en crear aplicaciones a la medida." />
  </head>
  <body class="dark:text-white">
    <div class="fixed inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full bg-[radial-gradient(100%_50%_at_50%_0%,rgba(0,163,255,0.13)_0,rgba(0,163,255,0)_50%,rgba(0,163,255,0)_100%)] dark:bg-neutral-950 dark:bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_80%_80%_at_50%_-20%,rgba(120,119,198,0.3),rgba(255,255,255,0))]"></div>
    <Header />
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl p-4">
      <article class="h-screen flex items-center flex-col justify-center">
        <h1
          class="typing-text bg-gradient-circle bg-clip-text font-black text-transparent border-r-4 text-6xl sm:text-8xl md:text-9xl dark:border-white overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          ALAN.DEV
        </h1>
        <section class="my-4">
          <p class="mb-2 text-center text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
            Soy <em class="font-bold">Alan Mayorga</em>. Ingeniero TI con +3 a침os de experiencia, principalmente enfocada
            en el desarrollo web.
          </p>
          <section class="flex justify-center gap-3 p-3">
            <SocialPill
              href="https://github.com/AlanMayorga"
            >
              <GitHub class="w-6 h-6" />
              GitHub
            </SocialPill>
            <SocialPill
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alan-mayorga/"
            >
              <LinkedIn width="24" height="24" />
              LinkedIn
            </SocialPill>
            <a href="http://" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"></a>
          </section>
        </section>
      </article>
      <Technologies />
        <Section id="experience" title="Experiencia" class="mt-0">
          <BriefCaseIcon slot="icon" class="size-9" />
          <article class="mb-4">
            {
              experience.map(({ title, company, date, responsibilities, achievements }) => (
                <Experience title={title} company={company}  date={date}, responsibilitis={responsibilities} achievements={achievements} />
              ))
            }
          </article>
        </Section>
        <Section id="proyects" title="Proyectos">
          <CodeIcon slot="icon" class="size-9" />
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            {
              projects.map(({ title, description, github, img, site }) => (
                <Card
                  title={title}
                  description={description}
                  github={github}
                  site={site}
                  img={img}
                />
              ))
            }
          </div>
        </Section>
        <Section
          id="about"
          title="Acerca de mi"
          content={[
            "+3 a침os de experiencia como Front End Developer donde tambi칠n he cumplido con la funci칩n de Full Stack Developer. Siempre me aseguro de utilizar las mejores pr치cticas de desarrollo para cumplir con los objetivos esperados del proyecto, y as칤 garantizar la satisfacci칩n del cliente. Estoy dedicado a la mejora continua de mi habilidad y conocimiento en el desarrollo de software para crear soluciones innovadoras y eficientes.",
            "Me gusta escuchar musica y hacer deporte, ademas de comer mucho (hamburgesas 游땖), y de vez en cuando viajar y conocer lugares nuevos.",
          ]}
      >
      <UserStarIcon slot="icon" class="size-9" />
    </Section>
    </main>
    <footer class="mx-auto my-0 max-w-screen-md p-3">
      <section class="text-center text-xs">
        Mi inspiraci칩n: <a
          href="http://midu.dev"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-blue-500">midudev</a
        > 游눞
      </section>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  html {
    font-family: 'Onest Variable', sans-serif;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  .typing-text {
    width: 8ch;
    animation: typing 2s steps(8), blink .6s infinite step-end alternate, waves 12s linear infinite;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    html {
      scroll-behavior: auto;
    }
  }

  @keyframes typing {
    from {
      width: 0;
    }
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    50% {
      border-color: transparent;
    }
  }

  @keyframes waves {
    50% {
      background-position: 9rem 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  const theme = (() => {
    if (typeof localStorage !== 'undefined' && localStorage.getItem('theme')) {
      return localStorage.getItem('theme')
    }
    if (window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches) {
      return 'dark'
    }
    return 'light'
  })()

  if (theme === 'light') {
    document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark')
  } else {
    document.documentElement.classList.add('dark')
  }
</script>